description.narrative: Improving efficiency of vaccination systems in multiple states through developing and operationalizing a web based Vaccine Logistic and Cold Chain Management system

condition.narrative: Social and environmental sustainability will be enhanced through application of the UNDP Social and Environmental Standards (http://www.undp.org/ses) and related Accountability Mechanism (http://www.undp.org/secu-srm).
UNDP as the Implementing Partner will comply with the policies, procedures and practices of the United Nations Security Management System (UNSMS.)

description.narrative: 1) Number of states that implement the electronic vaccine intelligence network (eVIN) 2) Number of Government Staff trained on the use of web and mobile based application for vaccine logistic management 3) Number of cold chain points equipped with temperature monitoring loggers
